{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium mobile-first comparison section titled:
    
    “Why Ariya Is Different”
    
    Subheadline:
    
    Most sleep supplements are designed to sell. Calm Nights was designed to work.
    
    Design Requirements:
    
    Clean luxury wellness aesthetic
    Ariya purple branding
    Rounded corners
    Mobile-first layout
    High contrast and easy readability
    Minimalistic design with plenty of white space
    Create a two-column comparison: “Calm Nights” vs “Other Brands”
    Use green checkmarks for Ariya
    Use muted gray or soft red X icons for Other Brands
    Keep the section compact and highly scannable
    Make this feel like a premium supplement brand, not an Amazon listing
    Comparison Rows:
    
    ✓ Fully Disclosed Doses
    ✗ Proprietary Blends
    
    ✓ Standardized Plant Extracts
    ✗ Non-Standardized Ingredients
    
    ✓ Melatonin-Free Formula
    ✗ Melatonin-Based Formulas
    
    ✓ Wake Up Refreshed
    ✗ Morning Grogginess For Some Users
    
    Design Notes:
    
    The four comparison rows should be the visual focus.
    Keep text short and easy to scan.
    Avoid large paragraphs.
    Add subtle shadows and rounded cards.
    Use a premium comparison table style similar to high-converting DTC wellness brands.
    Optimize specifically for mobile viewing.
    The section should feel trustworthy, clean, and modern.
    Make Ariya’s side visually stronger and slightly more prominent than the Other Brands side., Add a header row above the comparison table.
    
    
    
    Left column title: Calm Nights
    
    
    
    Right column title: Other Brands
    
    
    
    Make the Calm Nights header Ariya purple with white text.
    
    
    
    Make the Other Brands header light gray with dark text.
    
    
    
    Place the titles directly above their respective columns.
    
    
    
    Make the Calm Nights column slightly more visually prominent than the Other Brands column.
    
    
    
    Keep the comparison table mobile-friendly and easy to scan.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-comparison-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_mobile }}px 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-comparison-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-comparison-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_margin }}px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-comparison-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size_mobile }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtitle_color }};
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.table_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.shadow_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_blur }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-header-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.divider_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-column-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: {{ block.settings.header_padding_mobile }}px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.column_header_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ai-comparison-column-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}--ariya {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.ariya_header_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.ariya_header_text }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-column-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}--other {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.other_header_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.other_header_text }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-rows-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.divider_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.divider_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.table_background }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.cell_padding_mobile }}px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    min-height: {{ block.settings.min_cell_height }}px;
  }

  .ai-comparison-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }}--ariya {
    {% if block.settings.ariya_emphasis %}
      background-color: {{ block.settings.ariya_cell_bg }};
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-comparison-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size_mobile }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size_mobile }}px;
  }

  .ai-comparison-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}--check {
    color: {{ block.settings.check_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}--x {
    color: {{ block.settings.x_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.text_size_mobile }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-comparison-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_desktop }}px 40px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-column-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.header_padding_desktop }}px;
      font-size: {{ block.settings.column_header_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.cell_padding_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size_desktop }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.icon_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.text_size_desktop }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-comparison-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-comparison-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-comparison-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
